      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape! It has a few minor scuffs from typical daily use, but it runs beautifully and has been very well-maintained. If you're looking for a dependable vehicle that's ready to hit the road today, you\u2019re going to love this one. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
