    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This high-revving power unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system to deliver linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain consists of a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox paired with a variable M-differential lock for optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains composed with its original MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry. This example is mechanically sorted with a recently refreshed cooling system, including a new expansion tank and water pump, plus a comprehensive VANOS bulletproofing. While presenting with honest cosmetic patina consistent with spirited use, the subframe has been inspected and reinforced, ensuring structural rigidity for the next enthusiast owner.",
      "price": 31500.0,
