      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and comfort. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish, showing only the minor, expected signs of careful road use, with no significant dings or scratches to the bodywork. Inside, the cabin has been kept in stellar shape; the upholstery is free of tears or stains, and the dashboard remains crack-free. As a detail-oriented owner, I have ensured that every feature\u2014from the heated seats and sunroof to the touchscreen navigation\u2014is in full working order. Mechanically, the car is robust. It has a complete service history with recent oil and filter changes, a new battery, and brake pads that were replaced within the last six months. The tires have excellent tread depth, and the engine runs quietly without any leaks or warning lights. This car has been a reliable daily driver and is ready for its next chapter without needing immediate investment.",
